data.description: Welcome to this beautiful one story traditional home on Hannover Forest neighborhood with parks and pool. Brick on all exterior walls and two car attached garage. Open Floorplan with rounded corners and arches features both formals. Owner's suite, three guest bedrooms and two full bathrooms! 11 Feet ceiling Height in Living room and 9 Feet ceiling height in bedrooms. Large kitchen with gas range, Quartz counters, stainless steel sink and tile backsplash overlooks the family room. Breakfast room area features a glass door leading to a large covered patio!  Easy access to interstate 45 and 99. About 12 minutes drive to Woodlands Mall and 10 minutes to Exxon Mobile Campus
